# Alchemy Account Kit Configuration
# Get your API key from https://dashboard.alchemy.com/apps
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALCHEMY_API_KEY=

# Gas Manager Policy ID for sponsoring gas fees
# Configure at https://dashboard.alchemy.com/gas-manager
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALCHEMY_BASE_POLICY_ID=

# Platform Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLATFORM_NAME=doba
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=

# Site Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://doba.world
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=

## Setup Instructions

1. **Get Alchemy API Key**
   - Go to [Alchemy Dashboard](https://dashboard.alchemy.com/)
   - Create a new app or select existing
   - Copy the API key

2. **Setup Gas Manager (Optional)**
   - Go to [Gas Manager](https://dashboard.alchemy.com/gas-manager)
   - Create a new policy
   - Set spending limits and rules
   - Copy the Policy ID

3. **Update Contract Address**
   - Replace with your deployed doba contract address
   - Update chain ID if using different network
